  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Freighter Engine Flare Modifier</span>.<br><br>The extreme heat of the freighter's engines excites this filter of Emeril salts, tinting the exhaust with a vivid green hue.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your freighter at the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Upgrade Control Terminal</span> on the <VAL_ON>bridge<>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船驱动信号器修改器</span>。<br><br>货船驱动器的极度高温激发了这个艾梅里尔盐过滤器，使排气管染上了鲜艳的绿色。<br><br>在<VAL_ON>舰桥<>上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">升级控制终端</span>改变货船外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船引擎火光改造器</span>。<br><br>貨船引擎的極端高溫會和砪鹽產生反應，將廢氣染成鮮明的綠色。<br><br>可在<VAL_ON>艦橋<>上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">升級控制終端站</span>裡變更你的貨船外觀。"
  },
